{"id":"api/router/RouterFeatures","title":"RouterFeatures","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router/RouterFeatures\", \"name\": \"RouterFeatures\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/src/provide_router.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L704-L717\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/router/src/provide_router.ts#L704-L717\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"routerfeatures\">RouterFeatures<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterFeatures#routerfeatures\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一个类型别名，表示可与 <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> 一起使用的所有路由器特性。可以通过向 <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> 调用添加特殊函数来启用特性。请参阅每个符号的文档以查找对应的函数名称。有关如何使用这些函数，另请参阅 <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> 文档。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A type alias that represents all Router features available for use with <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code>.\nFeatures can be enabled by adding special functions to the <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> call.\nSee documentation for each symbol to find corresponding function name. See also <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code>\ndocumentation on how to use those functions.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/router/RouterFeatures\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterFeatures</a> = <a href=\"api/router/PreloadingFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">PreloadingFeature</a> | <a href=\"api/router/DebugTracingFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">DebugTracingFeature</a> | <a href=\"api/router/InitialNavigationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">InitialNavigationFeature</a> | <a href=\"api/router/InMemoryScrollingFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">InMemoryScrollingFeature</a> | <a href=\"api/router/RouterConfigurationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterConfigurationFeature</a>;\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterFeatures#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router\n - api/router/provideRouter\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/router\n - api/router/DebugTracingFeature\n - api/router/InMemoryScrollingFeature\n - api/router/InitialNavigationFeature\n - api/router/PreloadingFeature\n - api/router/RouterConfigurationFeature\n - api/router/RouterFeatures#routerfeatures\n - api/router/RouterFeatures#see-also\n - api/router/provideRouter\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/src/provide_router.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L704-L717\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/router/src/provide_router.ts#L704-L717\n-->"}